          <h3 style="font-size:clamp(18px,3vw,28px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.8px;margin-bottom:8px;">Three Horizons of Commerce</h3>
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;max-width:620px;">The commerce landscape is undergoing its most profound transformation since the invention of the shopping cart. Understanding the shift from human-driven to AI-augmented to autonomous isn't optional — it is the difference between leading your category and being disrupted by it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="th-grid reveal">
